{"tid":1012978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"開工利是2,000大元！信銀國際繼續闊綽 國泰僅派20蚊","createTime":"2019-02-08T04:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-08T04:43:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2455019c23b5ec12d636efe1a065ae29b89af0d0","tid":1012978,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190208/large/1549596659_f1fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190208%2Flarge%2F1549596659_f1fe.jpg&h=44fb74ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日大年初四，為不少公司首個開工日，各大公司陸續派出開工利是。其中，銀行界之中，中信銀行（國際）繼續闊佬，員工開工利是一如往年位位2,000元，信銀國際員工逾2,000人，料涉及開工利是超過400萬元！<br />\n<br />\n不過，信銀國際並非今年最闊綽，原因是長假期前，東亞銀行（023）已事先張揚為慶祝100周年行慶，大年初一派發位位3,888元大利是。<br />\n<br />\n金融界方面，康宏開工利是100元，涉及前線後勤員工共1,500人，年初七才開工。至於監管機構證監會則派50元。<br />\n<br />\n至於國泰航空（293），開工利是只有20元。"},{"pid":"3f393bca29066e52b0c89bd14f120ae35ae1acef","tid":1012978,"uid":93649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:29:14.000Z","msg":"咩啊 20蚊唔係錢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a463f7635673c6f1566483d4c623f506e6d9e64","tid":1012978,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:30:01.000Z","msg":"因報等陣又可以拎因航派利是少黎講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"013e9a2f4a5ea066233ac6c186a13b06259a05bb","tid":1012978,"uid":68132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2a463f7635673c6f1566483d4c623f506e6d9e64","tid":1012978,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:30:01.000Z","msg":"因報等陣又可以拎因航派利是少黎講 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-08T04:30:20.000Z","msg":"期待"},{"pid":"98e6bc846ea47d5f59a5f879dcddea3cdb863d91","tid":1012978,"uid":17443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019